&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Bartender | Intown Golf Club | Raleigh, NC&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;43&quot;&gt;($28.00 / hour + Premium Benefits &amp;amp; Perks Available)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;4&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Craft an elevated beverage experience behind our bar.&lt;/strong&gt; At Intown Golf Club (IGC), we are rewriting the script for private social clubs and luxury lifestyle brands. We are currently seeking a bright, focused &lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;4&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;212&quot;&gt;Bartender&lt;/strong&gt; to lead our beverage program on the floor. If you take pride in offering guests a diverse, seasonally inspired menu, warm conversation, and elite hospitality within a premium environment that respects your work-life balance, your next chapter starts here.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;What You’ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;6&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;6,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Elevated Mixology:&lt;/strong&gt; Mix, garnish, and serve premium alcoholic and non-alcoholic beverages, showcasing a deep knowledge of cocktails, beer, wine, and food pairings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;6,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Member Engagement:&lt;/strong&gt; Interact directly with members and guests, assessing their preferences, making expert menu recommendations, and nurturing a world-class bar experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;6,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Bar Operations:&lt;/strong&gt; Plan and present the bar menu, manage daily bar inventory, and restock supplies efficiently to ensure seamless shift execution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6,3,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;6,3,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Compliance &amp;amp; Cleanliness:&lt;/strong&gt; Maintain a pristine, organized, and deeply clean bar environment. Strictly check identifications to meet legal drinking ages and enforce total compliance with all local, state, federal, and IGC liquor regulations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;7&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;7&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;What You Bring:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;8&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;8,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;8,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;The Background:&lt;/strong&gt; Minimum of 2+ years of dedicated bartending experience within an upscale casual restaurant, fine dining establishment, luxury hotel, or private club.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;8,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;8,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;The Skills:&lt;/strong&gt; Deep expertise in premium cocktail creation, excellent physical stamina (ability to walk, stand, and carry heavy trays), and top-tier organizational abilities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;8,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;8,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;The Attitude:&lt;/strong&gt; A friendly, attentive, and highly professional demeanor with a natural passion for elevated hospitality.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;8,3,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;8,3,0&quot; data-index-in

&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job description&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;INTOWN GOLF CLUB LLC.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bartender&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Intown Golf Club is the premier private social club and lifestyle brand for people that appreciate the game of golf. IGC is seeking a bright mixologist who is always on the lookout for new beverage trends. For our bartender position, we&#39;re looking for a candidate who takes pride in offering our guests a diverse and seasonally-inspired beverage menu, a warm conversation, and helpful suggestions. When you shine, our guests will look forward to relaxing with you after a long day at the office.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bartender Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare alcohol or non-alcohol beverages&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interact with customers, take orders and serve snacks and drinks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assess customers’ needs and preferences and make recommendations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mix ingredients to prepare cocktails&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plan and present bar menu&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Check customers’ identification and confirm it meets legal drinking age&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restock and replenish bar inventory and supplies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay guest focused and nurture an excellent guest experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comply with all food and beverage regulations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bartender Requirements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+ years of experience in bartending.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent knowledge of in mixing, garnishing and serving drinks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to keep the bar organized, stocked and clean&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to walk, stand, and carry heavy trays.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A friendly, attentive attitude.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of cocktails, beer, wine, and food.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be the minimum age to serve alcohol.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A passion for providing customers with high-quality service.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Compliance with all local, state, and federal liquor laws.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Willingness to work at peak hours, which may include evenings, holidays, and weekends.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Medical/Dental/Vision insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;No Cost Teladoc Services (Mental Health Counseling/Dermatology/PT)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Paid time off&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Employee discount&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Pay: $28.00 per hour&lt;/p&gt;

