&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;2&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Dishwasher | Intown Golf Club | Raleigh, NC&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em data-path-to-node=&quot;2&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;44&quot;&gt;($17.00 - $20.00 / hour + Premium Benefits &amp;amp; Perks Available)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Looking for a kitchen that offers true structure, professional leadership, and respect for your time?&lt;/strong&gt; At Intown Golf Club (IGC), we believe a great member experience starts with a supported culinary team. We are a tech-forward, high-growth private social club (ranked #24 on the Inc. 5000), and we’ve traded the traditional, high-stress restaurant model for a culture focused on quality of life, clear communication, and service excellence. If you are a reliable professional who wants to work in a clean, organized, and collaborative kitchen where your contribution is truly valued, your next chapter starts here.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;4&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;What You Will Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;5,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;5,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Station Ownership:&lt;/strong&gt; Manage the thorough set-up, safe operation, and breakdown of the dishwashing station, keeping the kitchen stocked with clean cookware and the front-of-house stocked with plate ware, silver, and glass.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;5,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;5,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Environmental Cleanliness:&lt;/strong&gt; Maintain clean and dry kitchen floors, a sanitized dish area, and tidy loading, dumpster pad, and waste oil areas in strict accordance with State and County Health Department standards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;5,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;5,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Operational Support:&lt;/strong&gt; Complete all assigned opening, closing, and weekly deep-cleaning projects. Assist with basic food prep tasks, FOH/BOH cleaning, or office trash removal upon request.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;5,3,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;5,3,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Team Communication:&lt;/strong&gt; Maintain honest, open communication with coworkers and leadership, and consistently check out with a manager at the end of every shift.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;6&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;What You Will Bring:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;7&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;7,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;7,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;The Experience:&lt;/strong&gt; Previous back-of-house, dishwashing, or cleaning experience in a restaurant or hospitality environment is preferred, but a great work ethic is key.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;7,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;7,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;The Skills:&lt;/strong&gt; Strong physical stamina to stand for long shifts, handle heavy trash/waste oil removal, and maintain high sanitation standards under high-volume pacing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;7,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;7,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;The Mindset:&lt;/strong&gt; A punctual, reliable, and team-first attitude with a strong commitment to keeping the kitchen safe and organized.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt

&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job description&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;INTOWN GOLF CLUB LLC.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Server Assistant&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Intown Golf Club is the premier private social club and lifestyle brand for people that appreciate the game of golf. IGC is looking for an energetic and professional Server Assistant to join our vibrant restaurant. Your ultimate goal will be to provide our guests with outstanding customer service and actively help to improve their overall dining experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Server Assistant Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist customers with their orders by explaining specials, meals, and drinks, and make recommendations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver food orders to a variety of customers in a timely manner.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Accurately explain food orders to chefs, with specific attention to allergies and special requests.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help the wait staff set up tables by placing appropriate tableware, eating utensils, decorations, and napkins.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Uphold our food health safety and sanitation principles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Occasionally check on customers to handle any impromptu requests or issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Remove dirty dishes from the table.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Inform management on customer feedback.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Server Assistant Requirements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A minimum of 2 years’ experience in a similar role.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High school diploma or equivalent qualification is preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Outstanding communication and people skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to stay professional in a stressful work environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Superb multitasking skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Available to work different hours including weekends, days and nights.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Medical/Dental/Vision insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;No Cost Teladoc Services (Mental Health Counseling/Dermatology/PT)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Paid time off&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Employee discount&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Pay: $18.00 per hour&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Golf Services Associate | Intown Golf Club | Raleigh, NC&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;66&quot;&gt;($16.00 - $18.00 / hour + Premium Benefits &amp;amp; Perks Available)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;4&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Be the face of the ultimate member experience.&lt;/strong&gt; At Intown Golf Club (IGC), we are rewriting the script for private social clubs and luxury lifestyle brands. We are currently seeking an energetic, hospitality-driven &lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;4&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;214&quot;&gt;Golf Services Associate&lt;/strong&gt; to join our local operations team. If you are a team player who loves the game of golf, thrives in a high-end service environment, and wants a role with a premium organization that values your work life balance, your next chapter starts here.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;What You’ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;6&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;6,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;First-Class Hospitality:&lt;/strong&gt; Manage the bag drop and assist members and guests with their golf clubs, warmly directing them to their simulators, putting greens, locker rooms, or fitness facilities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;6,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Clubhouse Operations:&lt;/strong&gt; Maintain the pristine presentation of the putting green and all common outdoor/indoor areas, assisting the service and golf professional staff with quick facility upkeep between member groups.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;6,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Club Support:&lt;/strong&gt; Step in to assist with golf shop duties, manage member locker rooms, and ensure an elite standard of cleanliness and service throughout the entire facility.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6,3,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;6,3,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Team Alignment:&lt;/strong&gt; Work collaboratively across departments to uphold IGC’s core values and ensure a seamless, world-class club visit for every guest.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;7&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;7&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;What You Bring:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;8&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;8,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;8,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;The Background:&lt;/strong&gt; Previous clubhouse, golf course, or premium hospitality/customer service experience is preferred, but a natural passion for elevated hospitality is key.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;8,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;8,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;The Skills:&lt;/strong&gt; Outstanding communication and interpersonal skills, with a welcoming, professional, and approachable demeanor.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;8,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;8,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;The Flexibility:&lt;/strong&gt; Availability to work flexible hours, including days, nights, and weekend shifts to support club operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;9&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;9&quot; data-index-in-node

&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job description&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;INTOWN GOLF CLUB LLC.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Host/Hostess&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Intown Golf Club is the premier private social club and lifestyle brand for people that appreciate the game of golf. IGC Is seeking an experienced and driven individual for our Host position. We’re looking for someone who is a service focused multi-tasker, with strong guest service skills, who is committed to providing a high-quality experience to our patrons.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Host/Hostess Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide an excellent initial experience to patrons by greeting them and guiding them to their table in a very gracious manner&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide patrons with menus and answer any initial questions they may have&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with server staff to ensure timely greeting of patrons&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optimize dining room seating and coordinate with server and bar staff to ensure even and fair workload&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Answer phone and assist with reservation requests and questions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with member shop sales&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a clean reception area&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Host/Hostess Requirements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High School Diploma or equivalent&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous Host / Host Experience at a fine dining restaurant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to walk / stand for long hours.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exemplifies a history of service excellence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Extremely personable and have excellent communication skills (via phone and in-person)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong organizational skills with ability to monitor the entire dining and bar area&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Available to work at peak hours, which may include evenings, holidays, and weekends&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Benefits:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Medical/Dental/Vision insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;No Cost Teladoc Services (Mental Health Counseling/Dermatology/PT)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Paid time off&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Employee discount&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
